subject: College Athletics
Football
Heisman Trophy
lead_paragraph: Florida’s victory over L.S.U., No. 5 Texas’ 45-35 victory over No. 1 Oklahoma and No. 17 Oklahoma State’s 28-23 road upset of No. 3 Missouri provided yet another day of chaos.
